metadata.description: GROUNDED! From the pages of Guardians of the Galaxy, Rocket has found himself stuck in the LAST place he wants to be—the backwards, no-class, pit of a planet called Earth. It's where those dumb furry things people say he looks like are from! One thing is clear—it doesn't matter who or what gets in his way...he's gotta get off this mudball, NOW. Easier said than done.
metadata.name: Rocket Raccoon
